         The black ceramic band made by potters is the ultimate faction farming item.  Just look for some people killing giants anywhere (except IC) and ask if you can tag for faction.  The closer you get to the throne room or the temple in Kael the bigger the hit for each mob. Of course raiding Kael can be very rewarding so be sure to jump in on any raids you can.  </P><P>Also, once you are up to dubious you can do the first 2 steps of the Coldain Prayer Shawl quest over and over.  This seems to be a fairly good faction hit as well.</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=22254" target="_blank" target="_blank">Sssyx Syxyx</a><BR><a href="http://www.spiritofthemoon.com" target="_blank">Spirit of the Moon</a></P><P><a href="mailto:sssyx@mmdog.com">sssyx@mmdog.com</a></P><P><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
